# Tailwind CSS 4

- Tailwind v4 via `@tailwindcss/vite` in `astro.config.mjs`
- Global entry: `src/styles/global.css` with `@import 'tailwindcss'` and `@theme`
- Racing-italy palette: green primary (`#009246`), red accent (`#CE2B37`), light background only
- Prefer utilities and design tokens from `global.css`
